name: Michael
description:
I've been exploring the concepts of
Chaos and Order, of Consciousness
and Unconsciousness, questioning
the nature of reality. It is a dangerous
thing to do as at times it felt like I was
going mad. So along this journey of
discovery it is important to return to
one's identity. My name and my image
contains my identity. I'd encourage
everyone to embark on the
psychological adventure of Soul
Searching but frequently remind
yourself who you are or you risk
getting lost.
